						not include.\r\nExclude Product Status = ‘Default Only’ (X)

						‘Default Only’ (X)

						Outstanding Balances on active credit instruments where the
						Applicant type = P or S\r\nIf consumer is inactive for credit
						instrument, do not include.\r\nExclude Product Status = ‘Default
						Only’ (X)

						instrument, do not include.\r\nExclude Product Status = ‘Default
						Only’ (X)
